    ${valSubstr} =  Get Substring   ${valText}   0   3
    Log To Console  ${valSubstr}
    Log  ${valSubstr}
    ${sChangeVal} =  Convert To Number  ${valSubstr}
    Log     Osakkeen muutos ${sChangeVal}
    ${stuff}=  Catenate  ${osake}  ${sVal}  ${sChange}
